      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of luxury and dependability, perfect for someone who values a well-maintained machine. The exterior is finished in a deep charcoal metallic that still retains a high-gloss luster; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway commuting, the body panels are straight and free of any major dings. The alloy wheels are wrapped in premium tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seating surfaces are supple, showing only light softening on the driver's side bolster, and all power features\u2014including the sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system\u2014are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet. It has been serviced religiously at 5,000-mile intervals, with a comprehensive maintenance file included. Most recently, the vehicle received a fresh oil service, new filters, and a brake system flush. This is a turn-key car that drives as smoothly as it looks, offering a premium experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
