    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning driver. Combining robust mechanical integrity with a refined aesthetic, it offers a driving experience that remains both smooth and commanding. Every aspect of this automobile has been vetted to ensure it meets our exacting standards for safety and performance. Invest in a vehicle that balances sophisticated engineering with enduring value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
